decorations_added: Transform this modern open-plan 2-bedroom apartment exterior and living area into a Halloween spectacle: place carved glowing jack-o-lantern pumpkins on the outdoor dining table, kitchen island, and garden beds; drape realistic cobwebs across patio railings, glass windows, and tree branches; hang translucent ghost figures and bat swarms from the eucalyptus tree and overhangs; add purple, orange, and green spooky LED uplighting on the tree trunk, walls, and rooflines; create a mini graveyard on the lawn with tombstones, skeletons, and ground fog; project ghostly silhouettes on exterior walls; add spider props on stepping stones and minimalist skull accents on furniture for a sophisticated spooky vibe suitable for Oremeji Estate with nearby supermarkets and restaurants.
